::Shadow Wing::

She waited for the Preds to leave the area of the Ark.  She was 
wondering what they were up to. She knew Preds didn't just give 
anything away, let alone keep thier word.  Something was up, but she 
couldn't think of what it was. She was hoping Lunarpine was alright. 
She was starting to get worried about him.  He hadn't checked in for 
a while and it was bothering her.
